{"tid":176662,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陰毒","createTime":"2017-03-28T10:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T22:46:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d06331668faf8e151719afc3a75b947112c3eb93","tid":176662,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:20:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kowloonsingjai/?ref=br_rs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowloonsingjai%2F%3Fref%3Dbr_rs&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=23c1f9ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kowloonsingjai/?ref=br_rs</a><br />\n<br />\n城寨<br />\n4 hrs &middot; <br />\n<br />\n陰毒<br />\n<br />\n新特首已經選出，689應該做的是交接，但仍然出來搞鬥爭，一選完就拘捕佔中人士，今日又同馮煒光一齊插泛民，指「今次選舉，泛民不是根據信念和原則做人，只不過是策反曾俊華，分化建制派，期望「漁人得利，成功造王」，這裏面充滿政治陰謀和計算」。泛民唔出人是謀略，對方唔中計就媽人，儍的嗎？<br />\n<br />\n由今日到七月一日之後，689丶高佬和丶派錢同鄉會丶深圳大媽丶愛字頭仍然會繼續玩嘢，林鄭再唔切割，有排受，民望想起都難。"},{"pid":"488f3466374a98b694261d1bafe9a9abba63ee65","tid":176662,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T22:46:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}